{"id": 1853, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都识破了哪些租房信息里的小九九？", "description": "两年租房史，活活把我从小天真炼成火眼金睛。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 8998, "comment_count": 31, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170814163617dLgXynwufQSVHxci.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-15T17:00:11Z", "questions": [{"id": 2798, "title": "你都识破了哪些租房信息里的小九九？", "content": "你都识破了哪些租房信息里的小九九？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 229359, "content": "精装修，出租屋最低门槛，能住人的都叫精装修", "image": "img/option/option/20170815100358ShuYzpTVRXnygtf4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229388, "content": "首次出租：意味着可能连床都没有，一大堆要你自己添置", "image": "img/option/option/201708150946411yhUFa4vpqx9OSDu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229394, "content": "刚刚翻新：多半只是重新刷了个墙，卫生间马桶桶龄不下二十", "image": "img/option/option/201708150953443VR9TLA10H6CrdXa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229404, "content": "看房人超过 50 的人气房源：仍然没租出去，不是有硬伤就是太贵", "image": "img/option/option/20170814175056JPR0hD5TC6Busjzn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229407, "content": "房型正气：写了也不一定坐北朝南，但不写的很可能是朝向歪隔断乱", "image": "img/option/option/20170815100454IpPte01Qd9zCDhSo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229409, "content": "青年社区，酒店型公寓：餐厅厨房都在公共空间", "image": "img/option/option/20170814174706VAdh6i3wQ4IaN2C1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229411, "content": "中心城区，附近有商圈：不知道说的是哪个荒郊野岭的中心", "image": "img/option/option/20170815093611BAPskRySTJLrwmQd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229415, "content": "价位不高还号称紧临地铁：靠近地铁线最末端的站", "image": "img/option/option/20170815093951FSOz3c1bmoZ6MR4V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229417, "content": "紧凑型，超挤，厨房放了微波炉可能就放不下菜板", "image": "img/option/option/20170815100248yphg51OKTt6AxsQb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229420, "content": "实在没什么特色：“温馨居室“", "image": "img/option/option/20170814175641lF1PGirheaDpoNZm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229422, "content": "免中介费，房主直租：结果“房主”其实是二房东", "image": "img/option/option/20170814174439bl2Jc0yDtGKOM8uT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229529, "content": "高区阳光房，远离雾霾带：7楼老房无电梯", "image": "img/option/option/20170815150228HT4QjeEK7Jmfsr8c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}